This directory contains the kickstart files and scripts required to build the
CloudRouter live image and the CloudRouter virt images.


To build the Fedora virt image:

 make virt-img OS=fedora OS_VERSION=21 OS_TREE=http://dl.fedoraproject.org/pub/fedora/linux/releases/21/Server/x86_64/os/

To build the CentOS 7 virt image:

 make virt-img OS=centos OS_VERSION=7.1 OS_TREE=http://mirror.centos.org/centos/7/os/x86_64/

